      <title>泰国总理与央行的冲突升级令投资者担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/thai-pm-s-escalating-clash-with-central-bank-on-rate-cuts-worries-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理正在发起十年来最大规模的降息运动，加剧与央行的政策冲突，这可能会损害投资者对亚洲表现最差市场之一的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/thai-pm-s-escalating-clash-with-central-bank-on-rate-cuts-worries-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
